description: Toro Corp. acquires, owns, charters, and operates oceangoing tanker vessels and provides seaborne transportation services for crude oil and refined petroleum products worldwide. The company operates through Aframax/LR2 tanker and Handysize tanker segments. It operates a fleet of eight tanker vessels with an aggregate cargo carrying capacity of 0.7 million dwt. The company was incorporated in 2022 and is headquartered in Limassol, Cyprus.
